airtrafficcontrol.app.utils

Class ReportGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • airtrafficcontrol.app.utils.ReportGenerator

  • public class ReportGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Allows to emit various types of reports. These reports can be returned as an array of strings, or written out to files
    Author:
    Eva Gomes, Hugo Leal, Lucas Andrade
